snippet.title: Cursed to Golf Xbox Announcement
snippet.description:
Cursed to Golf is coming to Xbox!
Cursed to Golf is a golf-like adventure where every shot counts. With insane hazards, otherworldly power-ups and tons of replayability, will you make it out of Golf Purgatory or will you forever be… Cursed to Golf!?
#IDatXbox #IDXbox
